thread.title: Mrs Connie Downing
thread.title_full: Official Car Mats reviewed by Mrs Connie Downing

author: Mrs Connie Downing
title: Mrs Connie Downing
text:
Can't fault this firm or the product at all. The mats are of good quality, but more importantly, they fit perfectly and were less than 1/2 the price of mats from the dealer. Delivery was fast and excellent communication from the vendor.
Would order again if we need mats.
